e damage per second inflicted by the item will make your spend the collected gold to</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>get better and better and to become a legend ...</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145070/extras/670fb87f3a9b06aaa49f9e2993e0d994.avif?t=1771170315\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> Click and defeat powerful enemies.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>-15 unique Enemies.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145070/extras/09c3d39abb3165013c8ba2be81c7b4de.avif?t=1771170315\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>                                                     <u>Attention to the bosses!</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Need to do laundry or walk the dog?</strong> <strong>No worries!</strong> <strong>Your heroes will farm characters and automatically collect gold in your absence, even when the game is closed.</strong> <strong>But don't forget to come back and spend all that sweet gold on upgrades!</strong></p>",
